### Implement Common Segment Creation for Subscribers in Node.js

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

Standardizes segment creation logic across various instrumentation subscribers. A common `createSegment` function is introduced to handle segment initialization, attribute assignment, and starting the segment.

```javascript
// Example of a common createSegment function:
function createSegment(name, attributes) {
  const segment = new Segment(name);
  Object.assign(segment.attributes, attributes);
  segment.start();
  return segment;
}
```

