Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md

Downloads and launches Docker containers for all required services (Cassandra, Memcached, MongoDB, MySQL, Postgres, Redis) needed for testing the New Relic Node.js agent.

