### Log Process Exec Arguments (Node.js)

Source: https://github.com/newrelic/node-newrelic/blob/main/NEWS.md

Logs `process.execArgs` at the debug level. This can be useful for understanding how the Node.js process was started and what arguments were passed to the Node.js executable.

```javascript
console.debug(process.execArgs);
```

